menu "Matter Lock HomeKey"

config HOMEKEY_FACTORY_ISSUER_PUBKEY_HEX
    string "Factory issuer Ed25519 public key (hex)"
    default ""
    help
        Optional 32-byte Ed25519 issuer public key encoded as 64 hex characters.
        When set, the main ota_0 runtime seeds this issuer into the shared
        Home Key reader-data NVS model during boot.

        This allows the temporary ota_1 HomeKit provisioner to accept Apple's
        device-credential enrollment requests later, because those requests
        only carry an issuer identifier and not the issuer public key.

endmenu
